# skill: perf-validate
# purpose: Validate performance meets requirements (Performance Persona - Phase 4)
# triggers: Optimization complete

## Invocation
```
perf-validate <task-id> [--optimization <optimization-report>]
```

## Output
Creates: `memory/tasks/<task-id>/perf-validation.md`

## Implementation Flow

### 1. Final Verification
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# perf-validate.skill implementation

TASK_ID="$1"
OPT_REPORT="${2:-memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/optimization-report.md}"

echo "Running final performance validation..."
```

### 2. Generate Validation Report
```markdown
# Performance Validation: <task-id>

## Validation Summary
**Task:** $TASK_ID
**Validated:** $(date +%Y-%m-%d)
**Validated By:** <agent-name>

## Final Metrics

### Response Time
| Metric | Requirement | Baseline | Optimized | Status |
|--------|---|---|-|---|
| Average | <req>ms | <base>ms | <opt>ms | ✓/✗ |
| P95 | <req>ms | <base>ms | <opt>ms | ✓/✗ |
| P99 | <req>ms | <base>ms | <opt>ms | ✓/✗ |

### Throughput
| Metric | Requirement | Baseline | Optimized | Status |
|--------|---|---|-|---|
| Requests/sec | <req> | <base> | <opt> | ✓/✗ |

### Resource Usage
| Metric | Limit | Baseline | Optimized | Status |
|--------|---|---|-|---|
| Memory | <lim>MB | <base>MB | <opt>MB | ✓/✗ |
| CPU | <lim>% | <base>% | <opt>% | ✓/✗ |

## Improvement Summary
| Metric | Improvement | Target | Achieved |
|---|---|---|-|
| Response Time | <base>ms → <opt>ms | <target>% | ✓/✗ |
| Memory Usage | <base>MB → <opt>MB | <target>% | ✓/✗ |

## Optimizations Applied
1. <optimization 1> - <result>
2. <optimization 2> - <result>

## Remaining Concerns
| Concern | Impact | Recommended Action |
|---|---|-|
| <concern> | H/M/L | <action> |

## Load Test Results
| Scenario | Users | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|-|
| Normal Load | <n> | ✓/✗ | <notes> |
| Peak Load | <n> | ✓/✗ | <notes> |
| Stress | <n> | ✓/✗ | <notes> |

## Monitoring Recommendations
- [ ] Add response time metrics
- [ ] Add throughput metrics
- [ ] Add resource utilization alerts
- [ ] Set up performance regression alerts

## Sign-off
**Performance Validation:** ✓ PASSED | ⚠ ACCEPTABLE | ✗ FAILED

**Approved for production:** Yes/No

**Conditions (if any):**
- <condition 1>
- <condition 2>

**Next:** Handoff to dev-ship or perf-optimize
```

### 3. Checkpoint
```bash
if [ "$ALL_METRICS_PASS" = "true" ]; then
    checkpoint --phase custom --description "Performance validation passed for $TASK_ID" \
        --next "Ready for handoff to dev-ship"
else
    checkpoint --phase custom --description "Performance validation failed for $TASK_ID" \
        --next "Additional optimization required"
fi
```
